Z"/><meta itemProp="dateModified" content="2018-10-10T08:57:21.000Z"/><meta itemProp="commentCount" content="1677"/><div class="RichContent is-collapsed"><div class="RichContent-inner"><span class="RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText" itemProp="text">午觉醒来，摊在椅子上看消息，看到好几个人邀请我回答这个问题，于是赶紧把我自己扶了起来。 关于这个问题，关键词在<b>「伤害很大」。</b> 由于我无法判断，题主定义里的伤害「大」<b>究竟是个什么程度。</b> 所以从<b>两个角度</b>来回答一下。 如果你是担心：吃完泡面<b>生命安全会受到威胁。</b> 网上常流传着关于方便面的谣言，听起来确实很吓人。 比如：<b>「方便面有多种添加剂，32 小时都不消化，32 天才能解毒」。</b> 其实，食品添加剂并不是魔鬼，<b>只要使…</b></span><button type="button" class="Button ContentItem-more Button--plain">阅读全文<span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--ArrowDown ContentItem-arrowIcon" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24"><path d="M12 13L8.285 9.218a.758.758 0 0 0-1.064 0 .738.738 0 0 0 0 1.052l4.249 4.512a.758.758 0 0 0 1.064 0l4.246-4.512a.738.738 0 0 0 0-1.052.757.757 0 0 0-1.063 0L12.002 13z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></button></div><div class="ContentItem-actions"><span><button aria-label="赞同" type="button" class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--up"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--TriangleUp VoteButton-TriangleUp" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="10" height="10"><path d="M2 18.242c0-.326.088-.532.237-.896l7.98-13.203C10.572 3.57 11.086 3 12 3c.915 0 1.429.571 1.784 1.143l7.98 13.203c.15.364.236.57.236.896 0 1.386-.875 1.9-1.955 1.9H3.955c-1.08 0-1.955-.517-1.955-1.9z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span>赞同 <!-- -->31K</button><button aria-label="反对" type="button" class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--down"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--TriangleDown" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="10" height="10"><path d="M20.044 3H3.956C2.876 3 2 3.517 2 4.9c0 .326.087.533.236.896L10.216 19c.355.571.87 1.143 1.784 1.143s1.429-.572 1.784-1.143l7.98-13.204c.149-.363.236-.57.236-.896 0-1.386-.876-1.9-1.956-1.9z" fill-rule="evenodd"><